<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pilot Media & Business</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0f1115; color: #e5e7eb; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .bento-card { background: #1a1d23; border: 1px solid #2d3139; border-radius: 16px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .accent-blue { color: #3b82f6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4">
    <header class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase">Pilot<span class="accent-blue">Hub</span></h1>
        <div class="bg-blue-600/10 border border-blue-500/30 text-blue-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm mt-4">
            <marquee>Latest News: Campus infrastructure updates... Professional grooming sessions available...</marquee>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <section class="md:col-span-2 bento-card p-6 min-h-[300px] flex flex-col justify-end">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Modernizing Campus Welfare</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Strategic roadmaps for student life improvement.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="bento-card p-6 border-blue-500/50 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Executive Services</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Premium grooming and branding solutions.</p>
            <button class="bg-blue-600 w-full py-3 rounded-lg font-bold">Book Now</button>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="mt-12 text-center text-gray-500 text-xs">
        <p>© 2026 Daniel Chibueze Ugochukwu. Powered by Pilot Media.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
